## User Stories

---

### US-B04 — Researcher: Upload Revised Documents

> As a researcher, I want to upload revised versions of my application documents, so that I can respond to reviewer feedback without losing previous versions of my work.

---

### US-B05 — Ethics Committee Member: Provide Review Feedback

> As an ethics committee member, I want to provide structured feedback and comments on applications, so that researchers clearly understand required changes and improvements.

---

### US-B06 — Administrative Staff: Maintain Audit Trail

> As an administrative staff member, I want the system to automatically record all actions taken on applications (e.g., submissions, reviews, decisions), so that there is a clear and traceable history for accountability and compliance.
